{"id":537254,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/08/【图说天朝】触怒小粉红-老公变汉奸/","date":"2016-08-08T06:10:10Z","modified":"2016-08-10T00:20:11Z","title":"【图说天朝】触怒小粉红 老公变汉奸","content":"<p>8月8日，微博红人王思聪发表了针对“孙杨事件”（国内舆论批评霍顿夺冠后讽孙杨曾涉禁药）的个人看法，他认为一些网民强制要求霍顿道歉一事“拿出去使行不通”，并且截图发布了孙杨曾经的“国歌门事件”新闻。这番“不支持道歉”与“黑孙杨”的举动显然与“爱国政治正确”不符，王思聪的这两条微博因此受到了许多“爱国网民”的攻击。</p>\n<blockquote><p>@王思聪：呵呵，硬按着别人头让人道歉这事儿只有在中国才好使，拿出去使别人可不吃你那套呀。</p></blockquote>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-537258\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/6ce2a3d1gw1f6m77pkxcnj20c80ki0uv.jpg\" alt=\"6ce2a3d1gw1f6m77pkxcnj20c80ki0uv\" width=\"440\" height=\"738\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/6ce2a3d1gw1f6m77pkxcnj20c80ki0uv.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/6ce2a3d1gw1f6m77pkxcnj20c80ki0uv-179x300.jpg 179w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p>\n<p>以下为该两条消息下部分热门微博评论截图：（北京时间8日13时）</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-537262\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/王思聪评论.jpg\" alt=\"王思聪评论\" width=\"533\" height=\"895\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/王思聪评论.jpg 533w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/王思聪评论-179x300.jpg 179w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-537263\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/王思聪评论2.jpg\" alt=\"王思聪评论2\" width=\"533\" height=\"915\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/王思聪评论2.jpg 533w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/王思聪评论2-175x300.jpg 175w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1826792401/E2AljA7Qq\">传送门1</a>  <a href=\"http://weibo.com/1826792401/E2Ath4pfI\">传送门2</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627],"tags":[9971,31546,9431,11711,9465,9481,25466,31548,30636,31547,31559]}